    <section class="sectionWidth">
      <div>
        <h1 class="h1">#OpenBelgium22 on 29 April 2022</h1>
        <h2 class="h2 intro">
          Open Belgium is an annual community event, where we make Belgian
          knowledge open, usable, useful and used.
        </h2>
        <h2 class="h2 intro">
          Join us to discuss the future of
          <strong>Open, Privacy and Trust</strong> in Belgium in 2022 –
          <strong>live</strong> at “De Krook” in Ghent.
        </h2>
        <!-- <a target="_blank" href="https://form.typeform.com/to/S70tAdxS"
        class="button sessionButton">Submit a talk</a> -->
